This script allows you to leave loading till after the page has rendered

To use include the script in your header and then use the following:

jQuery.deferJSLoad('url.js');


To check the js has loaded and to bind further events use code like this:

function jsTest() {
  //example of lazyloaded fancybox plugin
  $('a.popup').fancybox();
}

$(window).bind('deferredJsLoaded', jsTest);
